Author: joe2x4#5987
Content:
So many friends are playing this fantasy "American" football league. I'm amazed at the level of dedication to this. 

It's got me thinking. How cool would it be if we started a "Komodo Fantasy League" asset chain. It could be a good opportunity to advertise Komodo brand, onboard new users, show off some crypto conditions, build team spirit, and gambling.
I'm betting that this could be mostly built from the existing CC rpc.
With oracle's it could take the shape of a crypto league, your chosen team of crypto vs another using metrics from say CMC to determine the winner. It could be any sport? The league could take the shape of anything goes, teams could be consisting of weather patterns, YouTube video game players, Trump tweets, stock markets, elections, comic book characters, etc, or even leagues vs other leagues.  
Just a fun seed I wanted to plant.
